stic ray-tracing models fit the Fe K lag well, with the best-fit giving\na compact X-ray source at a height of 5 gravitational radii and a black hole\nmass of 1.3e7 Msun.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 20 Nov 2013 18:27:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-18"}
