\\lesssim\\gamma\\lesssim10^{3.9}$ and\n$10^{6.6}\\lesssim\\kappa\\lesssim10^{8.8}$ which are independent of $r$ when\n$\\theta_{\\rm pl}\\sim1$ and $1+\\sigma\\sim1$ at $r_{\\rm LC}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Nov 2013 09:13:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-11-22"}
