 Anderson's theorem. Our results capture the\nkey experimental trends in the cuprates.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Nov 2013 10:19:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 Sep 2014 07:06:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-18"}
