ch that $H_\\theta u=Eu$; (3) The map\n$\\Phi_E$ is minimal iff $E\\in \\sigma(H)\\setminus\\{\\text{edges of open gaps}\\}$.\nIn particular, $\\Phi_E$ is minimal for all $E$ for which the fibered rotation\nnumber $\\alpha(E)$ associated to $(\\omega,A_E)$ is irrational with respect to\n$\\omega$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Nov 2013 13:16:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-11-22"}
