. Thus, we capture an amazing\nphenomenon, likely of a more universal character, where a peripheral vertex\nbecomes the one which is over dominating the complex network during an\nexceptionally long period of time.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Nov 2013 13:23:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 15 Feb 2014 12:56:43 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 18 Feb 2014 15:01:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-02-19"}
